name: 斯嘉丽·阿宾南特
name_full: 斯嘉丽·阿宾南特 Scarlett Abinante
introduction: Scarlett Abinante was born on March 24, 2011 in California, USA. Scarlett is an American Actress. She is best known for her role as Julia Cody in TNT's Animal Kingdom. She began her acting career portraying the role of Emma Boland on the television series Good Girls (2018). She made her professional acting debut in a 2018 short film Preschool in L.A. (2018). She also appeared on television series Team Kaylie (2019) & Disney Channel's Bunk'd (2015). She is the older sister of Actress Cosette Abinate. She also has two younger sisters who are also Actresses named Adele & Daphne.
